15:03.547 --> 15:06.515
King of the Jews.
Okay, that is it, Glenn!

15:06.517 --> 15:09.618
You need to stop being a whiny,

15:09.620 --> 15:11.586
snotty little baby man

15:11.588 --> 15:14.289
and get back to work,
or I'm going to write you up!

15:14.291 --> 15:15.790
Do you understand me?

15:16.593 --> 15:18.460
I said, "Do you understand me?"

15:18.462 --> 15:19.795
- Yes...
- What?

15:19.797 --> 15:21.930
- Yes. I said yes.
- Good.

15:28.906 --> 15:31.573
I liked "High Fidelity,"
but I'm not sure

15:31.575 --> 15:33.942
