you want to be in charge.

15:59.303 --> 16:00.769
That's not what I meant.

16:00.771 --> 16:02.838
Look, man, I get it. It's hard.

16:02.840 --> 16:05.407
One day you're on top of the
world, winning Grammys,

16:05.409 --> 16:06.842
