16:06.844 --> 16:08.977
forcing your music
onto people's iPhones...

16:08.979 --> 16:10.245
I'm not Bono!

16:10.247 --> 16:11.780
Okay, okay. What if we did, like,

16:11.782 --> 16:13.181
a Jimmy Kimmel kind of thing

16:13.183 --> 16:15.083
where we call people and we tell them

16:15.085 --> 16:16.685
that their kids are dead?
But then we're like,

16:16.687 --> 16:19.020
"Just kidding.
But they will be in 50 years

16:19.022 --> 16:21.523
if we don't take action
against climate change."

16:21.525 --> 16:25.227
Yes, I love it. Such a good idea.

16:28.332 --> 16:29.303
Knock-knock.

16:29.833 --> 16:32.200
Heard that Amy came down
pretty hard on you.

16:32.202 --> 16:33.802
Yeah, I bet you loved that, huh?

16:33.804 --> 16:36.037
What? Oh, come on. Give me some credit.

16:36.039 --> 16:37.873
I know we've had
our issues over the years,

16:37.875 --> 16:40.542
but I hate to see you
brought down like that.

16:40.544 --> 16:42.036
You think that's fun for me?

16:42.212 --> 16:44.546
- You're smiling.
- I'm always smiling.

16:44.548 --> 16:46.148
I'm a happy person.

16:46.150 --> 16:48.378
And I know what you're going
through, okay?

16:48.544 --> 16:50.977
I can only imagine how
hard it is that someone

16:50.978 --> 16:53.688
that you took under your wing
like a father and daughter

16:54.305 --> 16:56.124
would just rip into you like that.

16:56.409 --> 16:58.340
I mean, that's got to be a gut punch.

16:59.066 --> 17:00.395
What does it feel like?

17:00.397 --> 17:02.397
What? What?

17:02.399 --> 17:03.153
Just that...

17:03.575 --> 17:06.401
total, complete,
all-encompassing impotence.

17:06.403 --> 17:08.403
- You think I'm impotent?
- I don't.

17:08.405 --> 17:09.905
Oh... oh, no. Hold up!

17:09.906 --> 17:12.240
I will show you exactly
how impotent I am.

17:12.242 --> 17:13.909
- I'm gonna do something.
- Go. You should do it.

17:13.911 --> 17:15.577
- I'm gonna do something!
- Yeah, do it, Glenn!

17:15.579 --> 17:16.744
- I'm doing it!
- Do it, Glenn!

17:16.747 --> 17:17.483
I'm doing it!

17:18.848 --> 17:20.226
This doesn't concern you.

17:20.983 --> 17:21.970
Gotcha.

17:23.854 --> 17:26.354
I get that there's value
to spreading awareness

17:26.356 --> 17:28.690
and getting the word out.
I'm not opposed to that,

17:28.692 --> 17:30.091
but that can't just be all you do.

17:30.093 --> 17:31.993
That's just posturing.
You know, there's...

17:31.995 --> 17:33.228
there's the kind of people
who do things,

17:33.230 --> 17:34.896
and then there's the kind of people

17:34.898 --> 17:36.264
who talk about doing things.

17:36.266 --> 17:38.257
- And you're both of those?
- Exactly.

17:39.002 --> 17:40.902
- Well...
- Attention, shoppers.

17:40.904 --> 17:42.737
I would like to read to you from a book

17:42.739 --> 17:45.607
